pve-center (1.0.0-1) unstable; urgency=medium

  * v1.0 — Multilingual release (EN, RU, ZH, FR, ES, AR).
  * Full hardware config editor for running VMs.
  * Storage monitoring with usage charts.
  * VM migration, disk resize, snapshot rollback.
  * PVE firewall, SDN, Ceph, HA, replication management.
  * Language switcher in status bar.

